      "text": [
        "1093 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَنْ صَلَّى اَلصَّلَوَاتِ اَلْخَمْسَ جَمَاعَةً فَظُنُّوا بِهِ كُلَّ خَيْرٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1093 – He (as) said:\n\"Whoever prays the five daily prayers in congregation, assume every good about him.\""
        ]
      }
    }
